node.excerpt: Here it is, we are finally live! After lot of efforts and lot of contributions from the community we can now say we have officially started the Keycap-Archivist project! This started as a little proof of concept and ended up as being a usefull tool…

If you're in the artisan keycap hobby you may have seen sometimes a little prison or a cutted hand caps; those come from Cozcaps. He took some times to answer some questions for us. Enjoy! So let's introduce CozCaps, can you please present yourself…
